skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tedi e. p. g.
des: TeDi EPG provides users of Alexa devices the ability to find out what their favourite Television Channels are playing right at the moment or what is scheduled for the rest of the day. The Skill provides programme guide for almost all popular TV channels that is available in Sri Lanka.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
